oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Dance floor and main entrance to Dunbar Cave, Clarksville, Tenn.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Color tinted photograph of the dance floor and main entrance to Dunbar Cave State Park. There are tables and chairs spread throughout the space, and an unidentified man stands next to some (center). Postcard features a white border, divided back, and narrative on reverse.
